  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Cut your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into fries and add them to a baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Add a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
