    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile pat your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Chop the <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> in half widthways</p><p>Coat the <strong>chopped basa </strong>evenly in your <strong>red Thai curry paste</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
