    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span><strong> flour </strong>to a plate with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Press the <strong>chopped basa</strong> into the flour firmly to evenly coat all over</p><p>Meanwhile, peel and dice <strong>half</strong> your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>remaining shallot </strong>finely</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
