    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wipe the reserved pan clean and return it to a high heat</p><p>Slice your <strong>brioche bun[s] </strong>in half</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>brioche halves</strong>, cut-side down, and cook for 3 min or until coloured and charred on one side only</p><p>Once charred, remove and set aside until serving</p>",
